



RREQ received:
    1. Update routing table for reverse route
        *   if rreq.hops <= route.hops then update route
            * route.broadcast_id = rreq.broadcast_id
        *   NOTE if this is a new route      ex) never heard of rreq.src_ip before
        *   NOTE if rreq.hops < route.hops   ex) more eff. route
    2. RREP generation:
        a. If I have route to rreq.dst_ip then send RREP

    3. RREQ flooding:
        a. If either NOTE from 1, set the rrep_sent flag.
        b. send RREQ on all interfaces except the source.
        c. don't send rrep if already sent, unless NOTE from 1